column2: Parts of Brant, Waterloo, and Wentworth Counties
column20: Stereoscopic coverage. On verso: Royal Canadian Air Force, Crown copyright. Source: National Air Photo Library [Parts of Brant, Waterloo and Wentworth Counties] Operation VPH 252/51 Hamilton, May 14, 1951, September 9, 1951 and April 22, 1952.

column19: 1 remote-sensing image ; 19 x 24 cm. Some surface damage (coloured pens). Some shots partially obscured by cloud shadow.
column20: Shows parts of southwest Hamilton, west of James and south of Main. Includes Ancaster area. Includes construction of the Ancaster section of the Highway 403. Some are photocopies of originals from the Queen's University, Maps and Air Photos Collection. Source: [Ontario Department of Lands and Forests, Division of Surveys and Engineering, Aerial Surveys Section], November 1967.
